{"tid":1576481,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[人面識別] 你以為剩係電燈柱先有？黨企中國海外/中國建築地盤會裝人面識別系統","createTime":"2019-09-17T09:18:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T16:49:10.000Z","uid":307711,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0e0b1c83b51fbe5819714c8f634a739addca4c93","tid":1576481,"uid":307711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:18:38.000Z","msg":"朋友借account代post<br />\n<br />\n我係黨企中國建築裡面員工，公司有幾大，承接幾多香港地盤工程，相信唔使我多講！<br />\n<br />\n宜家公司計劃全面喺全港地盤門口安裝人面識別系統，用嚟代替返放工打卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4NMtEuH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4NMtEuH.png&h=05daee3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OMZSmH3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOMZSmH3.png&h=b8ae7d1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n負責人面識別工程的海宏公司，即係中國建築機械部，負責租設備比中國海外+中國建築，同埋提供設備維修及技術支援。換句話嚟講，所有人面訊息會落入呢間黨企手上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WXKi1L6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWXKi1L6.png&h=af31c12b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n截止2019年8月31號，註冊建築工人達到4x萬，在職計起碼都超過13萬人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qVAVjyL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqVAVjyL.jpg&h=548bd42a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hEjGe66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhEjGe66.jpg&h=5ec9a3ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁即係話，所有工人+員工只要發過夢，都有機會比人面識別到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，仲唔計為數眾多只係路過地盤的市民<br />\n<br />\n細死極恐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請廣傳話比全香港市民聽支共滲透已經無孔不入！！"},{"pid":"0cd77561861d62aeb4fa98fe7a79830ea8d58b5f","tid":1576481,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:19:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【922攻略流出】<br />\n907<span style=\"color: gold;\">加強版</span>配合hkmap live <br />\n更「大局」交通測試，彩虹戰衣、影帝、機巴、塞鐵、嶄新突擊RB、私家車傾巢而出，裡應外合 <br />\n+機場員工集體Call Sick <br />\n+雷達站/機場附近新搞作<br />\n+大量中港貨櫃司機加入物資支援！<br />\n<br />\n更多攻略，陸續公布，敬請留意"},{"pid":"f7c0cfd1ff79f891132ae0814b9bc2f89702d565","tid":1576481,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ded6ecbc8d2a6d2b719db5663d43dac86d2cc97","tid":1576481,"uid":307711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7c0cfd1ff79f891132ae0814b9bc2f89702d565","tid":1576481,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:24:50.000Z","msg":"Cam同人面識別系統兩樣野嚟"},{"pid":"6bb0c2f17a11e1e26360169ec372d6fd25551d73","tid":1576481,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ded6ecbc8d2a6d2b719db5663d43dac86d2cc97","tid":1576481,"uid":307711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7c0cfd1ff79f891132ae0814b9bc2f89702d565","tid":1576481,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:24:50.000Z","msg":"Cam同人面識別系統兩樣野嚟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:27:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"177865e5232a292148e3cf659ff1788464fa3a21","tid":1576481,"uid":307711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid